data.description: Welcome to your potential sanctuary in the highly sought-after Hilltop Manor community! Immerse yourself in the comfort of this meticulously curated two-story colonial, a perfect blend of ease and charm that promises to redefine your living experience.  As you step through the entrance, be embraced by the inviting ambiance created by gleaming hardwood floors and a kitchen bathed in the soft glow of recessed lighting. Intelligent storage solutions effortlessly merge style with practicality, offering a daily living experience like no other. The flexible layout invites you to sculpt the spaces to match your lifestyle – envision a cozy dining nook or a sprawling living area, the choice is yours.  Upstairs, a charming terrace beckons, unveiling breathtaking views of the Delaware River. The walk-up attic is a canvas awaiting your artistic touch, with endless possibilities to bring your vision to life. Practical features, including an outside basement entrance, a one-car garage, and a slate walkway, seamlessly complement the home's inherent charm.   But let's delve into the extraordinary features! Experience the timeless allure of a kitchen remodel approximately 8 years ago, revel in year-round comfort with a new central A/C unit, and rest easy with the security of an 8-year-old roof. The bathrooms exude contemporary elegance with new sinks and toilets, while a recently installed water heater adds the final touch to this exceptional package.  Envision yourself unwinding on the screened front porch, your private oasis in this exclusive community. Hilltop Manor, with its single entrance, ensures privacy and tranquility – a rare gem in today's bustling world.  In essence, this listing isn't just a property; it's an invitation to indulge in modern comforts in a timeless locale. Seize the opportunity to transform this exceptional residence into your own, where every feature has been meticulously crafted to elevate your living experience. Your dream home beckons – don't let it slip away! Explore the possibilities today and step into a new chapter of comfortable living.
